{"tid":543213,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"歡迎留低一個中/英文字詞上嘅知識","createTime":"2018-01-28T09:17:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T23:12:53.000Z","uid":154800,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cc02552c05b71e33e79c17cd75c4c56283d4cd06","tid":543213,"uid":154800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T09:17:02.000Z","msg":"寫/打啱啲字真係好緊要<br />\n一唔啱比人捉到就陰公<br />\n希望開個post集腋成裘，等大家知多啲可能成日錯，或者根本未聽過個字係咁用嘅case<br />\n<br />\n我知有啲人或者覺得，挑，呢啲唔係唔識啊話<br />\n不過你識又唔代表人識嘅，所以有啲咩特別嘅都可以留一留低<br />\n<br />\n拋一拋啲例子出嚟先<br />\n一、中文錯別字<br />\n<ins>百分之百</ins>vs<del>百份之百</del><br />\n<br />\n二、中文字讀音<br />\n希臘個「臘」字大家應該都係讀「立」?<br />\n<br />\n三、中文不常用字<br />\n跌宕（蕩）：事情多變，起伏不定<br />\n（呢個係歌詞有人用過先識..）<br />\n<br />\n四、中文估你唔到讀音<br />\n風靡一時，大家應該都會讀做風（魔）一時，但正音應該係風（美）一時，不過全世界都讀風（魔）個陣，你讀返正音未必聽得明<br />\n<br />\n五、英文易混淆字<br />\nadopt vs adapt<br />\nadopt：採取，收養<br />\nadapt：適應<br />\nThe suggestion proposed by him was adopted.<br />\nHe can hardly adapt to the new environment.<br />\n<br />\n六、英文字讀音<br />\nsuite：好多人可能見到佢就讀咗suit，但其實係讀sweet<br />\n<br />\n七、英文字重音擺位<br />\n有無人聽到人讀increase呢個字嘅時候，有啲會讀INcrease，有啲就讀inCREASE？呢個其實就兩個都啱，但睇下你咩情況用<br />\nINcrease：名詞<br />\ninCREASE：動詞<br />\n但有啲字例如triangle，就應該讀做TRIangle，讀triANgle就唔啱喇<br />\n<br />\n八、英文動詞時式轉換<br />\n例如seek，過去式應該係sought<br />\n<br />\n九、英文同義詞<br />\nbeauty，深啲嘅字就可以用pulchritude<br />\n<br />\n如果上面有錯希望大家可以幫手更正一下<br />\n其實呢啲都只不過係一小部分，希望大家可以交流下<br />\n等大家無論以後出post，又或者考試嗰陣都可以減低出錯機率<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48507bb769449896a0a8a5b39cc8fa2ce0839e94","tid":543213,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T09:17:58.000Z","msg":"Can嘅過去式係can"},{"pid":"4b930626b87641db6f9a932a83920f4081cb1a4d","tid":543213,"uid":31888,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T10:24:00.000Z","msg":"Archive <br />\nIg有呢個功能之後好多港女讀做achieve <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f11489a40bbc3beafffbff71ac8dcb13700a42a8","tid":543213,"uid":129039,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T10:50:01.000Z","msg":"可圈可點=值得讚揚 ✖值得斟酌"},{"pid":"b5f103cf5dae67cf40f99844876ab3b5dbd26d83","tid":543213,"uid":129039,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T10:51:45.000Z","msg":"人不為己 天誅地滅 嘅意思係人如果唔增進自己嘅修養就會畀天打雷劈<br />\n而唔係如果唔係以自己利益行先就會畀天打雷劈"},{"pid":"c0ed7c65902ce4b3985d4dd51eacb6c54f7fa93d","tid":543213,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T10:52:44.000Z","msg":"Goodest English"},{"pid":"d2e0e8138acf2022c8f20126f274c57ae83e8aaa","tid":543213,"uid":37719,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T10:55:20.000Z","msg":"禾<br />\n因為5小大陸人來左輕港而帶有國語口音，所以有「我」的意思"},{"pid":"df0a5b162112288e00f31b3ffcb69d4620b7d0b2","tid":543213,"uid":80140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T11:08:33.000Z","msg":"虫 係讀 「偉」<br />\n唔係讀蟲<br />\n小一教左記到而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"131708446c77b279ca9df66350af54402c3c767a","tid":543213,"uid":154800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T22:27:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nrevert：呢個字可能見到有人係email度用<br />\nI will revert to you as soon as possible.<br />\n但其實佢應該解做回復到舊時嘅狀態<br />\nReverting to an older iOS version seems to be more stable.<br />\n用嚟解做reply好似係印度英文嚟，好多人都認為唔啱，用返reply/get back會先啱"},{"pid":"45f25e992879582e73306ebfcf591022cf290c9d","tid":543213,"uid":156618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T23:31:17.000Z","msg":"留名學嘢"},{"pid":"740d532ea97060601ab43192b28289513377c86a","tid":543213,"uid":143292,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T23:48:11.000Z","msg":"discuss後面唔用about<br />\nO  We are going to discuss that issue.<br />\nX  We are going to discuss about that issue."},{"pid":"106d06ca7359340a70d4d98017fe4309434a5e8d","tid":543213,"uid":135776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T02:09:03.000Z","msg":"恁 係諗惗唸既正字"},{"pid":"419cc6cbe6d3e611f1a86b2c6f1ba168d25ebdf4","tid":543213,"uid":154800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T22:42:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好多時加un，dis，in都可以將個字變成反義詞<br />\n(in)valid，(in)tangible<br />\n但有啲字加完都係同一個解釋<br />\n(in)valuable，(in)flammable"},{"pid":"03abd5aa28fe93047e6612977a34afd8a56432d4","tid":543213,"uid":5375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"419cc6cbe6d3e611f1a86b2c6f1ba168d25ebdf4","tid":543213,"uid":154800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T22:42:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好多時加un，dis，in都可以將個字變成反義詞<br />\n(in)valid，(in)tangible<br />\n但有啲字加完都係同一個解釋<br />\n(in)valuable，(in)flammable"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T22:56:18.000Z","msg":"加a都得"},{"pid":"715dc23ce13468217b9e8412d1aac5c4e68ec8fa","tid":543213,"uid":123175,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T23:08:52.000Z","msg":"本字同末字都係木字加一橫<br />\n其一橫標示該字所代表部分<br />\n引說文解字<br />\n木上曰末<br />\n木下曰本"},{"pid":"617e549b32795319439cca50e8f51e5e34a1eede","tid":543213,"uid":35248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T23:12:53.000Z","msg":"沖涼搨骨、包剪搨、搨人個搨字係咁寫"}]}